of Odor Detection Specialists.

1000
00:42:44,086 --> 00:42:45,444
I don't know where he heard it from,

1001
00:42:45,445 --> 00:42:47,924
Supposedly, eating and drinking less

1002
00:42:47,925 --> 00:42:50,336
can help improve nose sensitivity.

1003
00:42:51,006 --> 00:42:52,284
Haiyang is not the same guy

1004
